    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年末の、ある日のこと",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\n今日は、事務所の大掃除をするんですよね？",
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。休みなのに、手伝いに来てもらって悪いな",
      "startTime": 8.000000012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、いつもこの事務所を使ってるんですから\n綺麗にするのは当たり前のことです",
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺と橋本さんだけじゃ絶対に終わらないから、助かるよ\n……ところで、そこの大荷物は一体なんなんだ？",
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "事務所の大掃除をするにあたって\n動画サイトで、お掃除の動画をいくつか観てみたんです",
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "プロ用の専用洗剤の威力に、隙間の埃を取るコツ……\n重曹がああも万能とは思いませんでした",
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "後はもう実践するのみと思って、紹介されていた洗剤や\nスポンジを買ってきたんです。そうだ、他にも――",
      "startTime": 45.4666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、沙季、気合いは十分伝わってきたから\nそろそろ始めようか",
      "startTime": 53.5855272822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、続きは実践で、ということですね\nでは、早速大掃除を始めましょう！",
      "startTime": 60.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}